snippet.title: Defend the Cake - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Defend the Cake is a scrumptiously strategic tower defense game. Take your time planning a maze of toast walls and delicious defenses. Then get ready to deploy your Eggbird minions in real-time to power-up your defenses and fend off the invading armies of bugs.

Download now on
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/674330/
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/defend-the-cake-tower-defense/id1317096823?mt=8
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.DefendTheCake.DefendTheCake&hl=en_US

Follow us on Twitter
https://twitter.com/DefendTheCake

Sign up for our mailing list to be the first to know about updates to the game
https://defendthecake.com/index.html#alpha
